---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import CTABand from '@/components/CTABand.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Group Retirement Savings Plans | Heidi Blondin Financial"
  description="Employer-sponsored group savings plans that help your team build financial security. Group RRSPs, DPSPs, and pension alternatives for Ontario businesses."
>

  <section class="bg-brand-plum py-20">
    <div class="container-content max-w-3xl">
      <h1 class="font-serif text-display text-white text-balance" style="font-optical-sizing: auto;">Group Retirement Savings Plans</h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-white section-gap">
    <div class="container-content max-w-3xl">
      <div class="font-sans text-[17px] text-brand-ink/75 leading-relaxed space-y-4">
        <p>The Canada Pension Plan (CPP) is designed to replace approximately 25% of employees employment income when they retire. But the average CPP payment is less that $600 per month. In order to retire comfortably, employees need to use other savings vehicles to fill this large gap in retirement income. Unfortunately, most Canadians are not saving enough on their own to fund their retirement.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-10 aspect-video w-full">
        <iframe
          class="w-full h-full"
          src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/IZK-5C4FKZ0"
          title="Group Retirement Savings Plans"
          frameborder="0"
          allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
          allowfullscreen
        ></iframe>
      </div>

      <div class="font-sans text-[17px] text-brand-ink/75 leading-relaxed space-y-4 mt-8">
        <p>The Canadian government passed the Pooled Registered Pension Plans (PRPP) Act in 2012, formally recognizing that greater access to workplace savings programs is needed to help Canadians adequately save for retirement. Other provinces are currently implementing Voluntary Retirement Savings Plan (VRSP) to comply with new provincial VRSP legislation.</p>
        <p>Ontario has not legislated a formal program to date, but an Ontario Pension Plan has been proposed along with discussion of PRPP and VRSP. As an employer in Ontario, there are many savings plan options available to make it easy for your employees to save for retirement. We can provide the information you need to help determine what plan is right for you and your team. We offer retirement savings plans, profit sharing, and pension plans.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-10 bg-brand-tintPlum p-6">
        <p class="font-sans text-[17px] text-brand-ink/75 leading-relaxed">Offering a Savings Plan to your employees will show that you care about their financial future.</p>
        <p class="font-sans text-[17px] text-brand-ink/75 leading-relaxed mt-4">Your employees will benefit significantly from their plan membership with:</p>
        <ul class="font-sans text-[17px] text-brand-ink/75 leading-relaxed mt-3 space-y-2 list-disc list-inside">
          <li>Reduced taxable income by having contributions deducted at source</li>
          <li>Lower investment management fees than they would pay in retail investment funds</li>
          <li>Access to leading Investment fund managers with no minimum investment requirements</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="font-sans text-[17px] text-brand-ink/75 leading-relaxed mt-4">These benefits will allow them to build greater retirement income for the future.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-brand-tintPlum section-gap">
    <div class="container-content max-w-3xl">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-h2 text-brand-plum mb-6" style="font-optical-sizing: auto;">At your Service</h2>
      <div class="font-sans text-[17px] text-brand-ink/75 leading-relaxed space-y-4">
        <p>At Heidi Blondin Financial, we will make administering your Group Savings Plan simple. We will also provide access to one-on-one financial advise for each of your employees. This will truly show your employees that you value their services and care about their financial future.</p>
      </div>

      <p class="font-sans text-[17px] text-brand-ink/75 leading-relaxed mt-8">Contact Heidi today to find a plan that is right for your team.</p>

      <p class="font-sans text-[17px] text-brand-ink/75 leading-relaxed mt-6">Group Benefit Plans are also available to compliment your group retirement savings plan offering.</p>

      <div class="mt-8">
        <a
          href="/contact"
          class="inline-block bg-brand-plum text-white font-sans text-sm font-semibold px-8 py-4 hover:bg-brand-plum/90 transition-colors"
        >
          Contact Heidi for Group RSPs
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
